data.description: Motivated Seller, BRING YOUR OFFER- NEW Price Improvement. One owner home. Wake up and savor a favorite morning beverage, as the beautiful sun rises from this Thornton home’s backyard view, listen to the frogs croak, and let the calmness of the morning send vibes of relaxation, before the start of the day.  This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home, located in Thornton, offers privacy from all sides, as the backyard opens to a small meadow, with no other homes behind it. It has a brand-new wooden fence to the North of the home’s backyard, and an easement to the right, for further privacy. New flooring, newly painted, newer A/C and HVAC, new screens, hard wired security system (will need to start service), are just a few of the features of this you will find, that make it move-in ready. Inside the garage, there is a built-in green house, with a mini-split a/c, where you can grow your own garden, or remove it to make it a two-car garage. The possibilities are endless, to make this a dream come true.
